name: Basingstoke 2049 #6
description: During lockdown I took several pictures while out and about in my local area. The emptiness of the usually bustling streets gave everything an almost apocalyptic feel and the haze took me to the world of Blade Runner 2049. In this limited series of 6 pictures I've tried to capture the 3 distinctive futurescapes depicted by one of my favourite cinematic experiences. They are very special to me.
